node.text: This a the subject we need more about please 🙏 God. BLESS
How does one go about back testing out life?

Life is a series pattern, a rhythm, a series of movements that, when seen without judgment, reveal the map to abundance. Every moment—every rise, every fall—has been a gift, guiding us to deeper wisdom. Just like in the stock market, trends emerge, showing us when to lean in, when to release, and when to expand.

Backtest your life. See the patterns not as mistakes, but as markers of your evolution. Walk in gratitude, unify the past, and step into the miracle that is already you.

Thank you, and I love you!
@sunhfarm yea will do!
Please speak more about this. Could you do a podcast episode expanding upon this concept?
@theshiftisreal360 on the way!
@abundance10000 🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾
GRAPHICS CLASS SIR!???😍
@riseandsoul ❤️❤️
Wild isn’t it. I share some of the experiences with you and the seeing of how it landed me here. 🤍
@shannxnquinn 🔥🔥🔥
Reflecting on those past versions and past traumas will help us realize the gifts within them all 🌟
Thank you and I Love you! Sent! 📨

Sooo good, everything is a frequency, and that is how something is created - it is a match to the feelings, thoughts, actions. 

Resonance is the key code to shift ✨❤️‍🔥 thank you for this brother!

@vibewithbonnieb yessss, I love this for you! Part of the magic of this world is simply (and not so simply, I’m afraid) BELIEVING in the first place! The Most High is ALWAYS in communication with us,  and unfortunately the way many of us ..including yours truly, were brought up…is thinking God only does BIG things…and DIVINE absolutely does, but more so…when we have faith and BELIEVE in ALL of the blessings we are given on a daily basis through downloads, signs, birds, music, numbers, Sean even…just all the things in all the ways…we are then gifted with more and more. Put your full belief, and gratitude in EVERYTHING you are given (down to half hour extra of sleep) and start seeing the beauty that is all around…the open communication that’s always been there for you…for all of us. Ase sister 💚
@thesolhighpriestessrising We are the de-coders and our power is the freedom to re-program the patterns into any condition we want. 🙌🏾
@_lolosade yes! Beautifully stated 💚

Everything we experience in this reality is simply a portal leading us into the next season …road signs and maps that are disguised as heart breaks and “rejections.” Everything about our existence is intentional, everything. The Creator and the created, the art and the artist…it is for us to see and discern the many signs and experiences, and then move the paint brush accordingly. Beautiful message as always, Ase 🪷
@abundance10000 I love this, and resonate deeply. Quantum Retrodiction embodied.
I don't have the memory to go to yesterday 😅
Powerful stuff. Do you have a template for this work? Pen and paper and start with timelines? I understand this is a prolonged process!
I’ve been looking at this and it’s mind blowing as I look back now like wow I went thru this to handle that and so on..Ty again for Sharing ♥️
This a the subject we need more about please 🙏 God. BLESS
Asantè ❤️
So bloody true!!! I have done it a few times and always shocked at the results
Wow! 🔥🔥
Thank you for this ❤️
Explain your back testing process??

Exactly:
Things don’t happen to you, they happen For you.
Your experiences are the foundation of who your are, you can built on top of it, or late it shake your reality in such a way that destroys you:
Suffer life or live life, your choice.
For most of us, once you can fully embrace what happened to you and forgive in your heart your parents and understand where they were coming from, and even thank them for everything they put you through, then you will know you have reached that point of no return where you see your life as abundance
Reverse Engineer, thats right 🗝️
Thank you Sean 🙏🏻
Absolutely 💯💯💯💯 how true this is!
